= Servers and Daemons =

Database:

 * mdbtools				# OOo2 supports the JET format
 * mdbtools-gmdb

Email:

 * fetchmail
 * procmail
 * exim4
 * exim4-daemon-heavy
 * exim4-daemon-light
 * dovecot-postfix

Must also consider webmail and so on...

VPN:

 * racoon # ipsec vpn

Web applications:

 * zope3-sandbox
 * python-moinmoin      # moin (>= 1.5)
 * python-django

Printing:

 * m2300w  # Driver for the Minolta magicolor 2300W/24000W color laser printers 
 * openprinting-ppds-extra          # Less common printer drivers we don't want in desktop

Utilities:

 * analog                 # essential for any web server, possible candidate for desktop integration
 * graphviz
 * logcheck		  # great security tool for any server
 * logcheck-database	  # useful for above
 * rrdtool
 * john

Radius server:

 * freeradius

Backup:

 * bacula-director-sqlite3
 * bacula-sd-sqlite3

Data trending:

 * cricket

Other:

 * sysvinit  # ScottJamesRemnant retain support for now

